<h1 id="인증서-확인">인증서 확인</h1>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">sudo </span>kubeadm certs check-expiration
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>/assets/images/views/kubernetes/kubeadm-certificate/
<img src="/assets/images/views/kubernetes/kubeadm-certificate/Untitled.png" alt="certificate check" /></p>

<h1 id="인증서-갱신">인증서 갱신</h1>

<p>CERTIFICATE AUTHORITY 파일들은 갱신이 되지 않음 - 기간이 10년임…</p>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">sudo </span>kubeadm certs renew all
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><img src="/assets/images/views/kubernetes/kubeadm-certificate/Untitled1.png" alt="certificate renew all" /></p>
